title: Famous Dubai chef 'Salt Bae' serves meal for Hollywood actor
text:
Famous Dubai chef 'Salt Bae' serves meal for Hollywood actor Web Team /Dubai Filed on February 3, 2017 | Last updated on February 3, 2017 at 11.48 am Share 
(@nusr_et/Instagram) When two famous people meet Notoriously famous for his trademark 'salt sprinkle' move, famous Dubai chef and butcher Nusret Gokce can add another famous figure to his portfolio. After meeting Bollywood's Sanjay Dutt and His Highness Sheikh Mohamed bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Crown Prince of Abu Dhabi and Deputy Supreme Commander of the UAE Armed Forces himself, the Turkish internet sensation is serving steaks for Hollywood actor Leonardo DiCaprio who was reportedly in Dubai last week. Leo in town: Is Leonardo DiCaprio in Dubai? In an Instagram post by Nusret, he is seen doing his trademark 'salt move' on the Hollywood actor's meal. The actor is visibly amazed and surprised; and we're pretty sure he enjoyed his dinner. After all, it's not every day that you have 'Salt Bae' as your chef. A photo posted by nusr_et (@nusr_et) on Feb 2, 2017 at 5:27am PST But Nusret's fame doesn't just end with celebrities. He has won over the entire internet becoming a cult icon. His signature move has been interpreted both in dance and in artworks. Jan 27, 2017 at 2:34am PST A photo posted by nusr_et (@nusr_et) on Jan 14, 2017 at 7:38am PST
